DDharmonize_validate_PopCounts

Source: R/DDharmonize_validate_PopCounts.R
DDharmonize_validate_PopCounts.Rd

This script implements a workflow for census population counts extracting from DemoData, harmonizing age groups, identifying full series, selecting preferred series, validating totals and by sex and eventually including key fields in the function output.
